item.excerpt:encoded: Food Express are proud to welcome Henry Savoy as the exciting new chef of this fresh bistro in the heart of the city.

item.title: Book early for your Christmas party
item.dc:creator: ozhef@hotmail.com
item.content:encoded: If youre looking for the perfect Christmas meal in Edinburgh, look no further than Food Express. Advanced booking is essential and with our amazing reputation and equally amazing food, places are going fast! To book your Christmas meal in the heart of Edinburgh, call us today to speak to a member of our friendly and dedicated team! Finally, from all of us at the Food Express, we wish you a Happy Christmas and we look forward to seeing you!

item.title: Grab tickets for "Mark Out"
item.dc:creator: ozhef@hotmail.com
item.content:encoded: We're proud to announce that Mark Out - the hugelypopular Scottish folk band will be playing a set here at Food Express on Saturday 18 July. There are limited tickets available so please speak with a member of the team if your interested in securing a front row seat to what's bound to be a fantastic night of music, food and drink!
